OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 31 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1986FBBC Two's new on-screen clock
OL,7,Faired for the first time at 1.05am on
OL,8,F31st March 1986, at closedown.
OL,9,
OL,10,FAnnouncer David Wheal was on duty:
OL,11,F"Well there's the first look at our new
OL,12,Fclock here on 2, which completes the
OL,13,Fbrand new image which I hope you like.
OL,14,FIf you do, then why not join us all
OL,15,Fagain at some point tomorrow..."
