OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 31 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2000FUK Arena is replaced by UK
OL,7,FDrama. UK Arena launched on 1st
OL,8,FNovember 1997, specialising in arts
OL,9,Fprogramming. The channel was part of
OL,10,Fthe UKTV network of channels. UKTV was
OL,11,Fa joint venture between the BBC and
OL,12,FFlextech. Poor ratings resulted in a
OL,13,Fshift of focus to drama and a
OL,14,Frebranding to UK Drama. It would be
OL,15,Frebranded again: first in March 2004 to
OL,16,FUKTV Drama and again in October 2008,
OL,17,Fto Alibi, from which point the
OL,18,Fchannel's focus was crime dramas.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG2003FThe subscription channel,
OL,21,FCarlton Cinema ceased broadcasting.
OL,22,
